Please note that you are purchasing a hand-poured candle. These products are not machine poured and mass produced. They are poured in small batches. Please keep in mind that you are purchasing a candle and supporting a small business. Your purchase supports individuals and the time we invest to create each item individually. 

For best results, trim your candle wick before each burn to ¼ inch above the wax, do not burn your candle for more than 4 hours at a time to prevent wick mushrooming and soot build-up that can shorten the life span of your candle. Please burn responsibly and adhere to the warning label, located on the bottom of your candle.
